F(\epsilon p)
 F(p)=\int_{-\infty}^\infty e^{ikpx}f(x)\;\mathrm{d}x 
 \begin{align} F(\epsilon p)&=\int_{-\infty}^\infty e^{ik\epsilon px}f(x)\;\mathrm{d}x\\              &=\int_{-\infty}^\infty e^{ikpx}f(x/\epsilon)/\epsilon\;\mathrm{d}x \end{align} 
